{"message": "computing sha1 hash for story", "source_id": "c2d69c69b1c16d147d0ea4b46d8fd784", "headline": "rolv LLC Launches rolvsparse\u00a9: A New Mathematical Operator That Makes Every Computer on Earth Run AI Faster -- With 99% Less Energy", "firstcreated": "2026-03-17T15:35:00Z", "hash_str": "b'{\"type\": \"text\", \"source_id\": \"c2d69c69b1c16d147d0ea4b46d8fd784\", \"headline\": \"rolv LLC Launches rolvsparse\\\\u00a9: A New Mathematical Operator That Makes Every Computer on Earth Run AI Faster -- With 99% Less Energy\", \"bylines\": null, \"firstcreated\": \"2026-03-17T15:35:00Z\", \"versioncreated\": \"2026-03-17T15:37:19Z\", \"originalfilename\": null, \"description_caption\": null, \"associations\": null, \"content_json\": {\"@xmlns\": \"http://iptc.org/std/NITF/2006-10-18/\", \"head\": {\"docdata\": {\"doc-id\": {\"@regsrc\": \"AP\"}, \"date.issue\": {\"@norm\": \"20260317T153500Z\"}, \"doc.copyright\": {\"@holder\": \"PR Newswire\", \"@year\": \"2026\"}, \"identified-content\": {\"classifier\": {\"@type\": \"apcategorycode\", \"@value\": \"f\"}}}}, \"body\": {\"body.head\": {\"hedline\": {\"hl1\": {\"@id\": \"headline\", \"#text\": \"rolv LLC Launches rolvsparse\\\\u00a9: A New Mathematical Operator That Makes Every Computer on Earth Run AI Faster -- With 99% Less Energy\"}}, \"distributor\": \"The Associated Press\"}, \"body.content\": {\"block\": {\"p\": [\"University of Miami Frost Institute independently confirms 50\\\\u00d7 speedups and 90\\\\u201399.9% energy savings across CPUs, GPUs, TPUs, and AI accelerators \\\\u2014 identical SHA-256 verified results on all platforms.\", \"FORT LAUDERDALE, Fla., March 17, 2026 /PRNewswire/ -- rolv LLC today announced the launch of rolvsparse\\\\u00a9, a universal software compute primitive that restructures matrix arithmetic at the mathematical level, delivering dramatic AI inference speedups and energy savings across every processor type with no hardware changes and no model retraining required.\", \"The insight behind rolvsparse\\\\u00a9 is straightforward: every AI processor on earth executes multiply-accumulate operations involving zero-valued weights \\\\u2014 calculations that contribute nothing to the output yet consume energy and time. rolvsparse\\\\u00a9 eliminates those operations mathematically, producing SHA-256-verified identical results in a fraction of the time.\", \"\\\\\"I don\\'t have any inhibitions,\\\\\" said Rolv E. Heggenhougen, Founder and CEO of rolv LLC. \\\\\"I don\\'t know what\\'s supposed to be impossible. So I just try things. When the math said it shouldn\\'t work on fully dense matrices \\\\u2014 where there are no zeros to skip at all \\\\u2014 I tried it anyway. It ran 63 times faster. That changed everything.\\\\\"\", \"RESULTS ON REAL PRODUCTION MODEL WEIGHTS:\", \"On a standard $1,000 consumer desktop PC at zero percent sparsity:\", \"On high-performance AI hardware:\", \"Because rolvsparse\\\\u00a9 is a mathematical solution rather than a hardware-specific optimization, the same software delivers identical\\\\u00a0gains across CPUs, GPUs, TPUs, and emerging accelerators \\\\u2014 with no modification required for each platform.\", \"INDEPENDENT VALIDATION:\", \"The University of Miami Frost Institute for Data Science and Computing independently confirmed all results are deterministic, reproducible, and produce identical SHA-256 cryptographic hashes across every tested processor class. No commercial relationship exists with rolv LLC.\", \"The full benchmark report, open verification tool, and validation letter are available at rolv.ai.\", \"ABOUT rolv LLC:\", \"rolv LLC is a Fort Lauderdale-based software company founded by Rolv E. Heggenhougen \\\\u2014 mathematician, serial entrepreneur, two U.S. patents issued, six pending, companies founded across four continents, two taken public. The company develops universal compute primitives for efficient AI inference. Complete IP portfolio available for acquisition or licensing.\", \"MEDIA CONTACT:\", \"Rolv E. Heggenhougen\", \"rolv@rolv.ai \\\\u2022 +1 954.253.4443\", \"rolv.ai \\\\u2022 @rolveitrem \\\\u2022 rolv.substack.com\", {\"a\": {\"@rel\": \"nofollow\", \"@href\": \"https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/rolv-llc-launches-rolvsparse-a-new-mathematical-operator-that-makes-every-computer-on-earth-run-ai-faster--with-99-less-energy-302716192.html\", \"#text\": \"https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/rolv-llc-launches-rolvsparse-a-new-mathematical-operator-that-makes-every-computer-on-earth-run-ai-faster--with-99-less-energy-302716192.html\"}, \"#text\": \"View original content:\"}, \"SOURCE ROLV, LLC\"], \"ul\": [{\"li\": [\"127\\\\u00d7 faster than the system\\'s own best software\", \"474\\\\u00d7 faster than the leading sparse library\", \"First-token latency 0.7ms vs 13.4ms\", \"99.2% energy reduction\"]}, {\"li\": [\"Up to 133.5\\\\u00d7 throughput speedup\", \"Up to 99.9% energy reduction\", \"Up to 100.9\\\\u00d7 faster first-token response\", \"Confirmed across large language models, mixture-of-experts architectures, and reasoning models\"]}]}}}}}'"}
